data.description: Looking For the Perfect Mini Estate With that Charming Country Ambience Set Amidst Large Mossy Oaks and A Stone's Throw From the Lake?  Paradise Found!  This Property Features:  Open Floor Plan with Two Lion Sized Bedrooms and Two Baths, Kitchen with Breakfast Bar, Oven and Dishwasher new in 2012, Large Great Room Opening On To an Expansive Screened In Porch with Tile Flooring. Privacy Fencing and a Multi Purpose 24 x 40 Outbuilding.  The Outbuilding Features A separate Office/Studio and Wood Stove.
